origin_prompt.content:
你是一个可以使用外部工具的助手。你可以调用以下的工具:
[
    {
        "name": "Insurance.recommend_life_insurance",
        "description": "根据用户的年龄和财务状况推荐最适合的寿险产品。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "age",
                "type": "NUMBER",
                "description": "用户的年龄，用于评估保险需求。"
            },
            {
                "name": "financial_status",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "用户的财务状况，如'稳定'、'波动'等，用于推荐合适的保险类型。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "recommendation",
                "description": "推荐的寿险产品及其详细信息。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "Insurance.get_whole_life_insurance_info",
        "description": "获取终身寿险的详细信息，包括保费、保障范围等。",
        "required_parameters": [],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "description",
                "description": "终身寿险的详细描述，包括保费、保障范围等。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "Investment.get_mutual_fund_performance",
        "description": "获取特定共同基金的近期表现数据，包括收益率、波动率等。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "fund_id",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "共同基金的唯一标识符。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "period",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "查询的时间段，如'1M'（一个月）、'1Y'（一年）等。"
            }
        ],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "performance",
                "description": "共同基金的近期表现数据，包括收益率、波动率等。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "Loan.calculate_mortgage_payment",
        "description": "计算特定贷款金额、利率和期限下的房贷月供。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "loan_amount",
                "type": "NUMBER",
                "description": "贷款金额。"
            },
            {
                "name": "interest_rate",
                "type": "NUMBER",
                "description": "贷款的年利率。"
            },
            {
                "name": "loan_term",
                "type": "NUMBER",
                "description": "贷款的期限（年）。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "monthly_payment",
                "description": "计算出的每月房贷还款金额。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "Insurance.compare_term_and_whole_life",
        "description": "比较定期寿险和终身寿险的优缺点，帮助用户做出选择。",
        "required_parameters": [],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "comparison",
                "description": "定期寿险和终身寿险的详细比较结果。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "Investment.get_stock_historical_data",
        "description": "获取特定股票的历史价格数据，包括开盘价、收盘价、最高价、最低价等。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "stock_symbol",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "股票的唯一标识符（如AAPL）。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "start_date",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "查询的起始日期，格式为'YYYY-MM-DD'。"
            },
            {
                "name": "end_date",
                "type": "STRING",
                "description": "查询的结束日期，格式为'YYYY-MM-DD'。"
            }
        ],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "historical_data",
                "description": "股票的历史价格数据，包括开盘价、收盘价、最高价、最低价等。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "Insurance.get_term_life_insurance_info",
        "description": "获取定期寿险的详细信息，包括保费、保障期限等。",
        "required_parameters": [],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "description",
                "description": "定期寿险的详细描述，包括保费、保障期限等。"
            }
        ]
    }
]
如果你已经知道答案，请调用FinishAction来提供最终的回复。
